---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CategoryGrid from '../components/CategoryGrid.astro';
---

<Layout title="台灣知識庫" description="開源、AI-friendly 的台灣完整知識庫，讓全世界認識真正的台灣">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <!-- 台灣山脈剪影背景 -->
      <div class="taiwan-mountains"></div>
      <!-- 台灣島輪廓 SVG -->
      <svg class="taiwan-silhouette" viewBox="0 0 100 100" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M30 20 C 35 18 40 20 42 25 C 44 30 46 35 48 40 C 50 45 52 50 50 55 C 48 60 46 65 44 70 C 42 75 40 80 35 82 C 30 84 25 82 22 78 C 19 74 20 69 21 64 C 22 59 24 54 26 49 C 28 44 29 39 30 34 C 31 29 30 24 30 20 Z" 
              fill="rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08)" 
              stroke="rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15)" 
              stroke-width="0.5"/>
      </svg>
      <!-- 流動漸層背景動畫 -->
      <div class="flowing-gradient"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="title-text">Taiwan.md</span>
        <span class="title-glow"></span>
      </h1>
      <h2 class="hero-subtitle">策展島嶼的深度敘事</h2>
      <p class="hero-description">
        開源、AI-friendly 的台灣完整知識庫<br>
        <span class="highlight">從多元觀點建構，為全世界策展台灣</span>
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#categories" class="btn-cta primary">
          <span>開始探索</span>
          <svg class="cta-arrow" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md" target="_blank" class="btn-cta secondary">
          <svg class="github-icon" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 0C5.374 0 0 5.373 0 12 0 17.302 3.438 21.8 8.207 23.387c.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23A11.509 11.509 0 0112 5.803c1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576C20.566 21.797 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>⭐ Star on GitHub</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">🏝️ 400+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">年歷史</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">🌿 59,000+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">物種</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">🗳️ 亞洲第一</span>
          <span class="stat-label">民主</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">🔧 90%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">全球先進晶片</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cover-story">
    <div class="cover-content">
      <h2>如何理解台灣？</h2>
      <p class="cover-lead">
        台灣是一座面積只有 36,000 平方公里的島嶼，卻裝著整個世界的複雜度。<br>
        四百年來，每一個踏上這座島嶼的人，都用不同的眼睛看見不同的台灣。
      </p>

      <div class="quotes-timeline">
        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">原住民族</span>
          <blockquote>
            「山川河流都是祖先的身體，我們是大地的孩子。」
            <cite>— 泰雅族口傳文學</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1584</span>
          <blockquote>
            「Isla Hermosa」— 美麗諸島。
            <cite>— 西班牙文獻，最早以「美麗」稱呼台灣的確切記錄</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1697</span>
          <blockquote>
            「水沙連內山，山盡處有大潭，廣可數十里。中有嶼，番人聚居之。」
            <cite>— 郁永河《裨海紀遊》，清朝文人的第一手台灣觀察</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1926</span>
          <blockquote>
            「勇士當為義鬥爭！」
            <cite>— 賴和〈覺悟下的犧牲〉，台灣新文學之父</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1946</span>
          <blockquote>
            「台灣人的悲哀，在於不知道自己是誰。」
            <cite>— 吳濁流《亞細亞的孤兒》</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">2013</span>
          <blockquote>
            「看見台灣，你會發現，這片土地比你想像的更美麗，也比你想像的更脆弱。」
            <cite>— 齊柏林《看見台灣》</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">當代</span>
          <blockquote>
            「海浪的記憶比人長。」
            <cite>— 夏曼·藍波安《天空的眼睛》，達悟族海洋文學</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-closing">
        <p>
          從南島語族的創世到半導體帝國的崛起，從戒嚴的沉默到亞洲第一個同婚合法化。
          台灣的故事不是一條直線，而是一張網。
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Taiwan.md 不是要給你答案。</strong>
          我們想做的，是給你一張地圖——一張讓你自己走進台灣的地圖。
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="cover-link">閱讀完整引言集 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2 class="section-title">為什麼需要 Taiwan.md？</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>策展式觀點</h3>
          <p>精心策展的深度敘事，不是百科全書式羅列</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>AI-Friendly 設計</h3>
          <p>結構化內容，讓AI也能理解台灣的複雜性</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>雙語國際視野</h3>
          <p>從在地觀點出發，用國際語言說台灣故事</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📚</div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>完整多面向</h3>
          <p>涵蓋12+領域，呈現台灣的立體完整面貌</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="language-statement">
    <div class="language-inner">
      <h3>🖊️ 為什麼用繁體中文？</h3>
      <p>
        Taiwan.md 選擇以<strong>繁體中文</strong>作為預設語言，這不只是技術決定——這是一種文化宣言。
      </p>
      <p>
        繁體中文是世界上仍在日常使用的最古老書寫系統之一，而台灣是全球唯一將繁體中文作為官方文字的主要使用地。
        每一個筆畫都承載著千年的文化記憶。當你打開這個網站看到漢字，你正在閱讀的不只是文字，而是一個活著的文化遺產。
      </p>
      <p>
        我們同時提供<a href="/en">英文版本</a>，但堅持讓繁體中文站在前面。
        AI 看得懂，搜尋引擎看得懂，而你——如果看不懂也沒關係——這份美麗本身就值得被看見。
      </p>
      <p class="language-en">
        <em>Taiwan.md is written in Traditional Chinese by default — the world's oldest writing system still in daily use, 
        and Taiwan is its last major home. We offer an <a href="/en">English version</a> too, 
        but we believe our language deserves to stand front and center. 
        Even if you can't read it, its beauty speaks for itself.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="categories" id="categories">
    <div class="categories-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">探索台灣</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">選擇您感興趣的面向，開始深入了解台灣</p>
    </div>
    <CategoryGrid />
  </section>

  <section class="contribute">
    <div class="contribute-content">
      <h2>加入我們</h2>
      <p>Taiwan.md 是社群驅動的開源專案。無論您是台灣本地人還是對台灣感興趣的國際朋友，都歡迎貢獻您的知識與觀點。</p>
      <div class="contribute-buttons">
        <a href="/contribute" class="btn btn-primary">麻瓜貢獻指南</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">
          GitHub 專案
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ===== HERO SECTION ===== */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    background: 
      /* 深層底色 */
      radial-gradient(ellipse 120% 80% at 50% 20%, #1a202c 0%, #0f172a 40%, #0a0f1a 100%),
      /* 細微紋理 */
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.02) 0%, transparent 30%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.015) 70%, transparent 100%);
    color: white;
    margin: -2rem -1rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: 
      /* 光暈層 */
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 80%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
      /* 星空效果 */
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 20px 30px, #ffffff, transparent),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 40px 70px, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.8), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 90px 40px, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.6), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 130px 80px, #ffffff, transparent),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 160px 30px, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.7), transparent);
    background-repeat: repeat;
    background-size: 200px 100px, 200px 100px, 200px 100px, 200px 100px, 200px 100px, 200px 100px, 200px 100px;
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0.4;
    animation: starsMove 20s linear infinite;
  }
  
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  /* 台灣山脈剪影 - 更層次感 */
  .taiwan-mountains {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 40%;
    background: 
      /* 遠山（最淡） */
      radial-gradient(ellipse 1000px 100px at 5% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.04) 0%, transparent 80%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 800px 120px at 15% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.06) 0%, transparent 75%),
      /* 中山 */
      radial-gradient(ellipse 700px 160px at 35% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 600px 180px at 55% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1) 0%, transparent 65%),
      /* 近山 */
      radial-gradient(ellipse 500px 200px at 70% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      /* 最近山（最深） */
      radial-gradient(ellipse 400px 220px at 85% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15) 0%, transparent 55%);
  }
  
  /* 台灣島輪廓SVG - 更精緻 */
  .taiwan-silhouette {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15%;
    right: 8%;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    opacity: 0.3;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2));
    animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  /* 流動漸層背景 - 更細膩 */
  .flowing-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.02) 0%,
      rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.03) 20%,
      rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.02) 40%,
      rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.015) 60%,
      rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.025) 80%,
      rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.02) 100%
    );
    background-size: 600% 600%;
    animation: gradientFlow 15s ease infinite;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  /* 標題設計 - 更精緻的品牌感 */
  .hero-title {
    position: relative;
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: "Noto Serif TC", 'Inter', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  
  .title-text {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg, 
      #fbbf24 0%, 
      #f59e0b 25%, 
      #dc2626 50%, 
      #b91c1c 75%, 
      #7c2d12 100%
    );
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    z-index: 2;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3));
  }
  
  .title-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #f59e0b, #dc2626);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    filter: blur(30px);
    opacity: 0.2;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  /* 副標題 - 更有氣勢 */
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: "Noto Serif TC", 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #cbd5e1 50%, #94a3b8 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-shadow: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  /* 描述文字 - 更精緻 */
  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #f1f5f9;
  }
  
  .hero-description br {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 50%, #dc2626 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  
  /* CTA 按鈕升級 - 更突出精緻 */
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .btn-cta {
    padding: 1.4rem 3rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 30%, #991b1b 70%, #7c2d12 100%);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 
      0 8px 32px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.4),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
    transition: left 0.6s ease;
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #b91c1c, #7c2d12);
    mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    mask-composite: exclude;
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary:hover::before {
    left: 100%;
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b91c1c 0%, #991b1b 30%, #7c2d12 70%, #5c1a1a 100%);
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 
      0 12px 40px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.5),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    box-shadow: 
      0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 
      0 12px 40px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }
  
  .cta-arrow {
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary:hover .cta-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px) scale(1.1);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.secondary:hover .github-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
  }
  
  /* 統計數字 - 更精緻設計 */
  .hero-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .stat {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    background: 
      linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 
      0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  
  .stat::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
    mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    mask-composite: exclude;
  }
  
  .stat:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    background: 
      linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 100%);
    box-shadow: 
      0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }
  
  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 50%, #dc2626 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
